# Debate Arena - Proposer agent

NAME proposer

INPUT task

GOAL argue """
Construct a compelling argument IN FAVOR of: $task
Structure:
1. Opening statement (clear thesis)
2. Three main arguments with evidence/examples
3. Preemptive rebuttal (anticipate the strongest counter-argument)
4. Closing statement
Use logic, data, and concrete examples. No straw men.
Acknowledge complexity — the strongest arguments are nuanced.
""" -> argument

RUN main USING argue
